OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening, with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain soon becoming confined to western
OL,8,Fhills, accompanied by hill fog.
OL,9,FElsewhere, conditions will be
OL,10,Fgenerally dry, particularly in the
OL,11,Feast. Breezy over hills. A warm night
OL,12,Ffor some in the south.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FFairly cloudy at first but
OL,15,Fbrightening up quickly, with spells of
OL,16,Fhazy sunshine developing along the
OL,17,Fcoast. Feeling pleasantly warm in a
OL,18,Flight breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
