OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday, cloudy to start with sunny
OL,7,Fintervals later. Wednesday and
OL,8,FThursday becoming sunnier and dry with
OL,9,Flight and variable winds. Temperatures
OL,10,Fvery warm.
